## Reproducibility

Steps to run the pipeline:

1. Clone repository
2. Install dependencies

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3. Configure database credentials

```
Config/database.yaml
```

4. Run ingestion pipeline

```
python SRC/Data/load_raw_to_staging.py
```

